u đó đã cùng nhau điều tra sự thật về cái chết của Lôi Nhất Phỉ.</p>","tmdb_id":139797,"cast":["Đàn Kiện Thứ","Kim Thế Giai","Trương Bách Gia","Chu Gia Kỳ","Lục Nghiên Kỳ","Tần Hải Lộ","Zhou Yanchen","Zheng Yunlong","Tạ Khả Dần"],"director":["Hình Kiện Quân","Trương Dực Vân"],"keywords":[],"tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"139797","season":1,"vote_average":7.4,"vote_count":30},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Đàn Kiện Thứ","name_vi":"Đàn Kiện Thứ","name_original":"Tan Jianci","tmdb_id":2122379,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3TxJqYIDQM3BOicpjAjSMr88bja.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2122379"},{"name":"Kim Thế Giai","name_vi":"Kim Thế Giai","name_original":"Jin Shijia","tmdb_id":1480174,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/q8vtZEynxIODbPDIRUellNufUHH.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1480174"},{"name":"Trương Bách Gia","name_vi":"Trương Bách Gia","name_original":"Zhang Bojia","tmdb_id":1989509,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/npWWY3WIwYXItHJ0MGjAHsSKGZd.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1989509"},{"name":"Chu Gia Kỳ","name_vi":"Chu Gia Kỳ","name_original":"Zhu Jiaqi","tmdb_id":1684719,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/26CqzL9FxkjjQiZXYkewDqXSbvo.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1684719"},{"name":"Lục Nghiên Kỳ","name_vi":"Lục Nghiên Kỳ","name_original":"Lu Yanqi","tmdb_id":2317989,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mX7isDFH6NlXzZhLZnHTUFpdKo9.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2317989"},{"name":"Tần Hải Lộ","name_vi":"Tần Hải Lộ","name_original":"Qin Hailu","tmdb_id":124992,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uhiUlT5c5RU3Qmo42Kjtm8gZRy.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/124992"},{"name":"Zhou Yanchen","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zhou Yanchen","tmdb_id":2082540,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tO6R8vx3jJsaOhCRPE7PvGUWsU9.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2082540"},{"name":"Zheng Yunlong","name_vi":null,"